text: Just emailed him :) all and any effort counts

My best friend got accepted for transfer to her dream university! I went straight to a 4-year out of high school whereas she stayed back in our home town going to a community college and it caused so much depression for her. I’m just so proud of her to see her hard work pay off :) <3
